	   <tr><td colspan=2>That was a good description on the use of Bonds of Force.&nbsp;&nbsp;However with one small alteration, the true power of BOF is unleashed.  <br><br>It's an AE spell, what other AE spells do we have? Direct Damage Ones.<br><br>Snare 3-4 Blue Mobs (Helps if they're the same type or run at the same speed).<br>Then use the previously mentioned kiting method, only this time replace the DD spell with a AE DD.<br><br>Why rake in 1 blue kill exp when you can rake in 4 blue kill exp simultanously.<br><br>Of course you need to test it out and see how creatures react to the snare, wether they all get snared or 1-2 resist it.  If 1 does resist, that starts a nasty run.  Always keep gate memed.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
