	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would be hesitant before stepping in with an AE and trying to take out a whole train of MOBs at once by myself. If you read my AOE post from before, you'll see that most AOE spells effect a limited number of targets. Same is true of Bonds of Force and it's upgrade, Atol's. Chances are you aren't going to get the whole train in either of them, and the stragglers will beat you up. So unless you're very confident in your abilities, or you're in an area /very/ green to you, I'd leave trainbusting to people who can take a few hits.<br><br>Cryselle Silverwynd<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
