	   <tr><td colspan=2>At level 29, I started kiting everything in sight.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have found that if you run too far, and you are "Out of Range" that running more will not solve anything.  Instead, do what i do, and click like a madman until your spell starts casting.  This will save you a lot of time, and if you just keep running, you might run out of room, and into a zone border, which could cause problems.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
